{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b609b13696","title":"批评《人民日报》不应“反冒进”（传达纪要）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"27635ea60e","index":0,"year":1958,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"b609b13696","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ad5e32a352","type":"title","text":"批评《人民日报》不应“反冒进”（传达纪要）","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9df9f2f853","type":"paragraph","text":"大家对报纸的反映比较好，报纸有进步，新闻，评论都有进步，不要满足。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69b923261d","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻近来搞得比较活泼。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d83dad865","type":"paragraph","text":"评论大家写，各版包干的办法是好办法。总编辑是统帅，要组织大家写，少数人写不行。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4904e62fe3","type":"paragraph","text":"组织形式，这种生产关系有没有妨碍生产力的发展，要研究。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25b645f8a4","type":"paragraph","text":"各部门、各版可以竞赛。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"955cebe3a0","type":"paragraph","text":"写评论，要结合情况和政治气候。转变要快。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d587ebae6","type":"paragraph","text":"写的不要刻版，形象要多样化。，","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bad1e86120","type":"paragraph","text":"政论要像政论，但并不排斥抒情。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce20dac872","type":"paragraph","text":"报社的人要经常到下边去，呼吸新鲜空气，同省委关系要搞好．","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"916813934c","type":"paragraph","text":"下去的人，又作工作，又当记者，不要长住北京，要活动一些，要经常到外边跑一跑．","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a09aea067","type":"paragraph","text":"人民日报是中央一个部门，同中央组织部，宣传部一样，都应该向地方学习．报纸一个很重要的任务是转载地方报纸的新东西，把这件事当作一个政治任务来作。这样，对地方报纸是鼓励，使他们非看人民日报不可。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba1483bd75","type":"paragraph","text":"思想评论可以搞。","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f676567668","type":"paragraph","text":"红专还是大问题，但要结合当前情况谈。","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"468c220d91","type":"paragraph","text":"标题要吸引别人看，这很重要。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4b3dfe35f","type":"paragraph","text":"除四害还要搞一个专刊。","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65d01c6cc2","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ccfb270ae","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年六月以后宣传反冒进的情况如何，要检查一下。检查那时的评论与消息。","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78a3dd1bb5","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二十日社论有原则性错误。说什么既要反对保守主义，又要反对急躁情绪。当时反右不到半年，这篇社论就以为反右成绩很大，估高了，是不对的。不能说这社论一点马克思主义没有，但“但是’以后是反马列主义的。社论的提法同魏忠贤的办法一样。东林党里有君子也有小人，朝廷里有小人也有君子。他的意思其实是说东林者小人。引我的话，掐头去尾，只引反“左”的两句，不引全段话，这不对。像秦琼卖马，减头去尾，只要中间一段。方法是片面的。前面讲少数如何，后面讲多数如何，形式上两面反，实际上是反“左”反“冒进”。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8928d1c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"批评双轮双铧犁“冒进’了，说南方不能用，不好．实际是用了，很好．应翻案。为它恢复名誉。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f96c9f9cf8","type":"paragraph","text":"“打破常规”的问题，社论说是“不适当地打破常规“，这话就不对。革命，就要打破常规。作为方针来讲，不能讲“反冒进”，只能讲“调整”。作为倾向来反，就把多快好省反掉了。","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1dfc1e2344","type":"paragraph","text":"社论说，特别在中央提出“多快好省”，“四十条”后，产生了冒进。这说法是片面的，这样说就认为缺点来自中央。","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34d0dbbb23","type":"paragraph","text":"你们反了右没有？这种说法，形式上是辩证的，实际是把辩证法庸俗化了。反“左”，反右同时并举，四平八稳。","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"813883db41","type":"paragraph","text":"“多快好省”方针本身是全面的，是一个整体，不能说这个适当，那个不适当。","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5409c4412","type":"paragraph","text":"根据经验，工作中有缺点是正常的，不是反常的。革命就是要跳跃。个别缺点不可免．要分清是九个指头，还是一个指头。工作中左一点，右一点，是正常现象。问题在于方针、方法如何．以后不要提“反冒进”，决不要提。","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"b609b13696","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":656,"end":654}}}},"__N_SSG":true}